textBeforeTable: Affinities Alilat can be found during shuffle time in the Yomotsu Hirasaka dungeon or by fusion. How to Obtain "The Arabian mother goddess, also known as Allat. The Black Stone at the Kaaba was thought to be her residence. She and her son, Dusura, were worshipped there by desert nomads." Info Alilat is a persona of the Empress Arcana.
